9	// - Applies isJumelee divisor (semi-detached roof is shared with neighbour).
10	// - Calls k-NN sizing on 1620 Reonic projects.
11	// - Computes financials (price, payback, CO2).
12	// - Returns the full BOM the UI / 3D scene consumes.
